2:
Yahweh is a jealous God and avenges; Yahweh avenges and is full of wrath;
\q Yahweh takes vengeance on his adversaries, and he continues his anger for his enemies.
\q

10:
For they will become tangled up like thornbushes; they will be saturated in their own drink;
\q they will be completely devoured by fire like dry stubble.
\q
